'''[[Mexico]]''' competed at the '''[[1936 Summer Olympics]]''' in [[Berlin]], [[Germany]]. 32 competitors, all men, took part in 15 events in 8 sports.<ref name="sports-reference">{{cite web |url=https://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/countries/MEX/summer/1936/ |title=Mexico at the 1936 Berlin Summer Games |accessdate=12 January 2015 |work=sports-reference.com}}</ref>
