'''Sport Vereniging Cosmos''', known as '''SV Cosmos''', is a [[Suriname]]se [[football (soccer)|football]] club. They play their home games in [[Paramaribo]] at the [[Dr. Ir. Franklin Essed Stadion|Frank Essed Stadium]].

They were [[relegated]] from the [[Hoofdklasse (Suriname)|Hoofdklasse]] in 2006–07<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.rsssf.com/tabless/suri07.html |title=Surinam 2006/07 |first=Karel |last=Stokkermans |publisher=Rec.Sport.Soccer Statistics Foundation (RSSSF) |date=18 September 2008 |accessdate=2 April 2015}}</ref> and again relegated, from the [[SVB Eerste Klasse|Eerste Klasse]], the following season.<ref>{{cite web |url=https://int.soccerway.com/national/surinam/eerste-klasse/2007-2008/regular-season/r6082/tables/ |title=Suriname Eerste Klasse 2007/2008 |website=Soccerway |publisher=Perform Group |accessdate=2 April 2015}}</ref> The club were formerly known as S.V. Road, before changing their name to Cosmos.

